divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my bedroom I live on the beach in a condo I saw this very bright bright lite coming from the west and I opened the window to get a better look with my banocqulers and I did not see any blinking lites that a plane has and I than ran to my balcany on the sea side of the condo an watch it till it got to the harizin then it took off in a second 3peaple coming off the beach also saw it an made a comment that if we report this they will tell us that it was a weather balloon. I know that it was not aplane or anything I've ever seen before, and I was a scout sniper in the US Marine Corps an i know what planes an helicoptors look like an this was nothing I've ever seen
